title: Eden Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Opened Oct 2015 in the same building complex as Manik Salon and Your Time Spa. Offers healthful meals with labeled vegan and gluten-free options, plus smoothies, coffee, and chocolate drinks. Kefir yogurt and kefir soda are made in-house.
streetAddress: Jl. Batu Bolong 8, Kuta Utara, Canggu
